{"tid":2034754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無外國國籍就得返香港政黨可以入？錯啦！你還有國際政黨","createTime":"2020-05-25T12:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T13:44:25.000Z","uid":91721,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"95cba787172b5d01604d1b25fe8926d7a4f2d8fe","tid":2034754,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:17:03.000Z","msg":"其實除咗外國政黨會有海外分部之外，大家可能都忘記咗世界上有國際性政黨呢樣野。<br />\n<br />\n世界上唔同國家嘅政黨都可能會有同一個意識形態，而呢啲就形成咗國際政黨組織。<br />\n<br />\n等我介紹下其中兩個啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fnvm8zf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffnvm8zf.png&h=f0337327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">海盜黨國際</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好見呢個黨個名onon99就以為佢哋係玩膠，其實佢哋係以革新版權制度同埋維護個人私隱嘅政黨嚟。<br />\n<br />\n海盜黨嘅主張主要有三個：一係改革版權法，二係廢除專利，三係尊重私隱。Rick Falkvinge（瑞典海盜黨前主席）曾經表示：版權法嘅原意就係製造壟斷，而唔係保護作者；而家科技分發資訊成本極低，壟斷係毫無必要嘅，甚至為了保持版權嘅壟斷就必定會侵犯個人私隱。而專利制度亦同鼓勵創意無關，Rick 指出已經有研究顯示，使用專利制度嘅多數係大型公司，根本無助創意，只係增加小型公司嘅成本。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋嘅戰績都幾輝煌下㗎，好似捷克同冰島海盜黨就喺2017年大選攞到10%議席，瑞典海盜黨甚至入到歐洲議會！而近年成日串鳩中共，仲要令布拉格同台北結成姐妹市嘅市長，都係海盜黨㗎！<br />\n<br />\n下面我仲會再介紹多個政黨，不過大家而家睇完可以諗下，香港一定就係英國、中國或者美國嘅香港咩？點解香港唔可以成為一個真正嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">世界仔</span>，擁抱世界各地嘅價值呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">好啦其實我係標題黨，因為而家香港根據無咩國際政黨喺度我只係想拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"1545f3e3665ffa61614fb50fb951de6146662aa5","tid":2034754,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"幫自己留個名先"},{"pid":"b7402a2c1ea663f3c365465fc66550243b86e299","tid":2034754,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"d70a65d01cfa6c66e4a43bf1bc4d4b81cc5ee0d8","tid":2034754,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a551d2c8929f371a42b0105553fc148b33c4d621","tid":2034754,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d70a65d01cfa6c66e4a43bf1bc4d4b81cc5ee0d8","tid":2034754,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"貼錢都濟"},{"pid":"1cc1ad5e69813d9925590b78faa624a52c24c07e","tid":2034754,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"咁入唔入到？"},{"pid":"28042ab4881225c526ad0f11b224b83db4b45b83","tid":2034754,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/57/Global_Greens_logo.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F5%2F57%2FGlobal_Greens_logo.svg&h=135fae41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>全球綠黨</strong></span></span><br />\n綠黨一睇就知係一班環保撚。佢哋係一班對可持續發展好有執著嘅人。要成為一個綠黨中人，你首先要認同佢哋嘅全球原則，分別係<br />\n1）社會正義<br />\n2）可持續性<br />\n3）非暴力<br />\n4）民主參與<br />\n5）尊重多元<br />\n6）生態智慧<br />\n<br />\n講起綠黨就梗係要講下同樣好幫香港人嘅台灣綠黨，佢哋嘅主張基本上同全球綠黨原則相符。佢哋會支持同性婚姻、世界和平、反核電、廢死同埋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><span style=\"color: green;\">大麻合法化</span></em></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綠黨同中共嘅政治立場明顯唔啱牙，德國綠黨同台灣綠黨都曾經撐香港，屌鳩中國。 雖然佢哋都係左膠，但都左得有風骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d72a02c160c6dcf961471e78148363988e1c1d","tid":2034754,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"a43f7bc77f6b128bcb9d77527af3b9e8c1fb5fde","tid":2034754,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cc1ad5e69813d9925590b78faa624a52c24c07e","tid":2034754,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"咁入唔入到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"得<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘就係國際自由聯盟嘅個人成員"},{"pid":"7598d3a4e5ca0ab3618b0c4b10aa19a0376b6a05","tid":2034754,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1264855554008190977?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1264855554008190977%3Fs%3D21&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3lDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=c3e9746d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1264855554008190977%3Fs%3D21&h=81feb96d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1264855554008190977?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"eb014b7608330cac2921eeadb04f00a1625f5ddb","tid":2034754,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"算唔算外國勢力勾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d68edfbd14b0c23b8bf33c6e8f5f757374eeaeb","tid":2034754,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7598d3a4e5ca0ab3618b0c4b10aa19a0376b6a05","tid":2034754,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1264855554008190977?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1264855554008190977%3Fs%3D21&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3lDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=c3e9746d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1264855554008190977%3Fs%3D21&h=81feb96d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1264855554008190977?s=21</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ca0c0c608a357e7b5f96c0319379892ae30ee4"